REST (Representational State Transfer) ek architectural style hai jisme client aur server HTTP protocol ke through data exchange karte hain (mostly JSON format).

HTTP Methods Difference (With Real Use Case)
Method	Use	Real Example
GET	Data fetch	Get product list
POST	New data create	Register / Login
PUT	Full update	Update profile
DELETE	Delete data	Delete address

Code	Meaning	Real Example
200	Success	Login success
201	Created	User registered
400	Bad request	Missing password
401	Unauthorized	Wrong credentials
403	Forbidden	No access
500	Server error	Backend crash
